      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCcd3d7dc0250010058a7a8a10427928d2"></a>Refitting the water tank
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11238"> </a>Fit clip (1) on the long hose (5), then install the latter in the upper fitting of expansion reservoir (4).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11240"> </a>Fit clip (1) on the short hose (2), then install the latter in the lower fitting of expansion reservoir (4).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/note.jpg">Note
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11243"> </a>In case of problems when fitting the hoses on the relevant fittings, it is recommended to apply some RUBBER-SPECIFIC LUBRICANT
         on the fittings.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11246"> </a>Position clamps (1) as shown in the figure.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/note.jpg">Note
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11249"> </a>To position the lower clamp, refer to the indicated value.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11252"> </a>Tighten the clamps (5) to a torque of 1 Nm ± 10%.
         </div>
      </div>
