         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11259"> </a>Fit tank (4) and hoses (2) and (5).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11261"> </a>Start screws (3) and tighten them to a torque of 8 Nm ± 10%.
         </div>
      </div>
